creator: Papa Tech
descriptionHtml:
The reimagined Papa Pal app gives you the tools to help more Members and make new connections. The app has one goal: to give our Papa Pals the best possible experience. Get the access and info you need to make being a Pal easy and rewarding. New features:

• For Pals Only: The new Pal app is a dedicated app built just for Pals. Every screen and feature was designed based on Pal feedback and created to make visits easier and better.

• Access Your Dashboard: The Dashboard screen shows you everything useful in one easily accessible view. Keep track of upcoming visits, see recommended visits near you, and filter visits to find the ones that meet your needs.


• Browse Visits: Browse through every available visit, use the new Map view to see where they are located, and find your next ideal visit using the visit filters.

• Make One-Tap Video Calls: The next level of Virtual Visits is here to make it easy for Pals and Members to see each other and make stronger connections. As an added benefit, Members don't need an app to access the video call — they can simply tap a link. Easy on members, and more rewarding for everyone.

• View the Map: Now you can easily browse and book visits to minimize your commute with the new Maps feature. Use it to see available visits near you, and make planning your visits for the day a breeze.

• Filter Your Options: Advanced filters make browsing options quicker and easier because you’re only seeing the options aligned with your offerings. New filters include:
○ Tasks filter - choose the specific tasks you prefer to do.
○ Date filter - see all visits filtered by day for the next 2 weeks.
○ Time Block filter - filter by blocks of time, similar to setting your availability.

• Pal Levels: Level-up your Pal game — hit new heights of greatness (and selflessness!) as you complete more visits and climb Pal levels. Pal levels are a fun way to track your total visit hours completed. In the future, your Pal level will unlock additional benefits.

To learn more about becoming a Papa Pal, visit joinpapa.com today.

• For Pals Only: The new Pal app is a dedicated app built just for Pals. Every screen and feature was designed based on Pal feedback and created to make visits easier and better.

• Access Your Dashboard: The Dashboard screen shows you everything useful in one easily accessible view. Keep track of upcoming visits, see recommended visits near you, and filter visits to find the ones that meet your needs.


• Browse Visits: Browse through every available visit, use the new Map view to see where they are located, and find your next ideal visit using the visit filters.

• View the Map: Now you can easily browse and book visits to minimize your commute with the new Maps feature. Use it to see available visits near you, and make planning your visits for the day a breeze.

• Filter Your Options: Advanced filters make browsing options quicker and easier because you’re only seeing the options aligned with your offerings. New filters include:
○ Tasks filter - choose the specific tasks you prefer to do.
○ Date filter - see all visits filtered by day for the next 2 weeks.
○ Time Block filter - filter by blocks of time, similar to setting your availability.

To learn more about becoming a Papa Pal, visit papa.com today.

descriptionHtml:
Ready to earn money with flexible hours and make a difference in your community?
Become a Papa Pal.

To start helping others, download the Papa Pal app.

If you are a member who is eligible for Papa through your employer or health plan, visit the Papa Care app to get started.

Papa Pals get paid to help older adults and families with things like companionship, transportation, house tasks, and errands.

How it works:
• Browse nearby visits in the app and find the ones that work for you. Then,
just tap to accept.
• The Papa Pal app tracks your drive. All you need to do is show up on time,
and have a great visit. That’s it!
• You’ll earn an hourly rate, plus bonuses, and other incentives.
• Use the app’s dashboard to keep track of your upcoming visits, available
visits near you, and more.

We're committed to creating safe experiences that build trust between our Papa Pals, members, and Papa. To learn more, view our Community Standards at papa.com/community-standards

To learn more about Papa, visit www.papa.com
